recipesJson.name: Dirty Custard
recipesJson.author: 308_hobbiest
recipesJson.description: Rich vanilla custard, drizzled with Carmel, and blended with a bit of sweet tobacco.

reviews.text: Wasen't sure  I was going to like this one as I'm not a real big tobacco fan. I mixed it up anyway, and I'm glad I did because it is amazing! It's a very well blended style vape that has a nice balance of caramel, custard, tobacco, and vanilla. Thanks for sharing.
